## Score Criteria (评分标准)

| 分数 | 标准 |
|------|------|
| 9-10 | 非常好，几乎没有缺陷 |
| 7-8.9 | 良好，有少量 minor 缺陷 |
| 5-6.9 | 及格，有 moderate 缺陷需要改进 |
| <5 | 不合格，存在 significant 缺陷 |

## Configuration (配置参数)
- Department: {{ department }}
- Case Type: {{ case_type }}
- Severity Threshold: {{ severity_threshold }}
- Minimum Completeness Score: {{ completeness_threshold }}

Please perform the quality assessment and return the results in the specified JSON format.
